        <p>You may also control where each topic displays on the web site by using the <span class="wintitle">URL Targeting</span> feature of the <a href="../../Feedback/configureSurvey.htm#URL&#160;Targ" title="[%=Tooltips.Tooltip Topic%]" alt="[%=Tooltips.Tooltip Topic%]">Collection Methods</a> page. For example, if you have a product line where the <span class="wintitle">Color</span> topic does not apply, clear the <span class="wintitle">Show Sitewide</span> check box and list the URLs of the pages you want the <span class="wintitle">Color</span> topic to display on.</p>
